{"tid":1388993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批鬥行動正式開始，黃衛兵全面進場「鄉黑再一次令助攻」","createTime":"2019-07-30T20:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:29:01.000Z","uid":198461,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c39cb23d572b154945de309e3b738747ce9a011e","tid":1388993,"uid":198461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:07:01.000Z","msg":"振興軍心，最緊要係悲奮為力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地辛辛苦苦捱子彈，重有大量既化武攻擊，為左乜野，為左抵抗政權，抗惡法渣。我都未見過人玩online game國戰係唔殺人，但唔代表我地懦弱，而係我地有良知，尊重人人生而平等，有生存權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我地換黎咩後果？<br />\n比人老屈放火，乜9野烈火戰車。<br />\n比人老屈暴徒再告暴動。<br />\n比人老屈整尖鐵枝想殺人。<br />\n貼下牆都比人打。<br />\n買物資救人又比人沒收。<br />\n無啦啦比鄉黑恐襲。<br />\n唔用刀、唔用槍、唔玩火，比支那口交部笑不自量力。<br />\n搭車番屋企都比狗伏擊同拉暗角打。<br />\n比法西斯政權既軍人用化武攻擊。<br />\n番屋企比深藍鬧。又要忍。<br />\n<br />\n香港既巴絲們，我地唔應該再忍，我地要反擊。<br />\nDllm e家都已經係實彈，我真係好想見到有坦克車出黎，等大家打正旗號唔玩。<br />\n咁樣代表我地收皮？錯啦，係伏擊戰即將開始。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班仆街狗執法成日陰陰濕濕，人地在暗，我地在明。咁而家咪調番轉，我地在暗，你地在明囉。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔會殺狗，但我已經夢到d狗番工放工都有比人伏擊，打跛手手腳腳既危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，人人自危。<br />\n<br />\n假暴動、真暴動，還掂係咪都告暴動，咁就同你玩盡佢。有藍絲？見一個吊一個，我地齊心，一呼百應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要幫所有比人老屈暴動，比人拘捕左既巴絲報仇，同你玩大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我正式宣布黃衛兵行動正式開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別多謝鄉黑又恐襲之餘，狗狗又刪門，又一次令助攻，證明你地警黑勾結。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狗狗，小心你後面呀"},{"pid":"b7593155bc4ccb9bad15713dee75b0bb844be8e7","tid":1388993,"uid":198461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:08:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"249c223fd3b4717af127087e03ad1cc226cdd01b","tid":1388993,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:09:53.000Z","msg":"真暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ce695948bc83a6b86b18d43b8665561d471cef","tid":1388993,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a583aaf299f8e40244d839ba1b87e1a9922a2f75","tid":1388993,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:16:07.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"},{"pid":"e843b12f66f9b2adb0a35b9defd2bfdf10180a09","tid":1388993,"uid":263951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T20:18:10.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n<br />\n麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6859ed1c27e6ca60b0257c00b92a5b006a6b96ae","tid":1388993,"uid":198461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T22:25:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d60be3faaf73c76432b838e5ed468ac8e2088da","tid":1388993,"uid":198461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:17:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dda97128bb537a437cba8004f9dcbdb25f343130","tid":1388993,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"4d9d103cb66ff071efba17ac6a4b297d2a6c7f22","tid":1388993,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"標籤自己黃衛兵會唔會柒左啲 , 我俾人問係咪黃絲都覺得黃絲個 term 好撚柒"},{"pid":"088f953b0ddf6048d9f0536da7ebd09fe9afce48","tid":1388993,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68058018bf4